  "informal_statement": "For real-valued functions a, b on an arbitrary nonempty or empty Finset index set s, (sum_{i in s} a_i*b_i)^2 <= (sum_{i in s} a_i^2) * (sum_{i in s} b_i^2) -- the general n-term Cauchy-Schwarz inequality.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Direct application of Mathlib's Finset.sum_mul_sq_le_sq_mul_sq, the library's general finite Cauchy-Schwarz inequality.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem general_cauchy_schwarz (ι : Type) (s : Finset ι) (a b : ι → ℝ) : (∑ i ∈ s, a i * b i) ^ 2 ≤ (∑ i ∈ s, (a i) ^ 2) * (∑ i ∈ s, (b i) ^ 2)",
